All this explains the broad smiles on the faces of directors of Gazprom, numerous in lubmin, at the point of arrival gas.
The construction of this pipeline also represents a technical achievement.
The tube is made of steel submarine under cement to protect against the anchors of ships.
Be supported in the bottom of the Sea, to an average of 200 m deep.
To build it, it was necessary to avoid minefields dating from the Second World War.
"was necessary to remove or destroy one hundred of them, out of caution," says Jens Müller, spokesman for the society Nord Stream.
